# Ignore everything in this directory
*
# Except this file
!.gitignore
# Keep the keys directory present so Docker builds always have it in the
# build context (the actual key files remain ignored and are generated by
# `key_generation`). Without a tracked placeholder the directory is absent
# from fresh clones and the Dockerfile `COPY configuration/bin/keys/` fails.
!keys/
keys/*
!keys/.gitkeep
